Package com.google.inject.tools.ideplugin.results Description

Classes for representing and displaying the results of user queries to the plugin.

The ResultsHandler is notified by for example the BindingsEngine when results to a query by the user are available. It then passes them to the ResultsView (more accurately to the IDE specific implementation of the com.google.inject.tools.ideplugin.results.ResultsView) for display.

Results to user's queries are stored as Results objects which usually consist of CodeLocation objects on a per module context basis.
